modName: Folk of the Deep The Miraa people
summary:
I have attempted to add one of my made up races to skyrim in a lore friendly way.
<br />i give you the miraa. They are a semi aquatic race from a realm of oblivion that was meant to be forgotten. modeled after the wood elf and based on the dwemer they will make an excellent addition to anyone's skyrim playthrough.
descriptionHtml: warning: this mod may or may not be lore friendly and may lead to nausea, sweating, rage quits, super overpoweredness, angry homicidal aliakaans on helicarriers. Basically you're out of luck.
author: theweegee103
